msgstr "You are running WordPress version %1$s that is not supported by Wordfence %2$s. Wordfence features will not be available until WordPress has been upgraded. We recommend using the current version of WordPress, but Wordfence will run on WordPress version %3$s at a minimum."

#: lib/wfJavascriptBridge.php:967
msgid "The Wordfence Audit Log is a premium feature that records a history of events on your site to assist in monitoring for unauthorized actions or signs of compromise. Events can include everything from user creation and editing to plugin/theme installation and updates. All data captured for relevant events is saved remotely to Wordfence Central to prevent any tampering that may interfere with post-incident analysis and response."
msgstr "The Wordfence Audit Log is a premium feature that records a history of events on your site to assist in monitoring for unauthorised actions or signs of compromise. Events can include everything from user creation and editing to plugin/theme installation and updates. All data captured for relevant events is saved remotely to Wordfence Central to prevent any tampering that may interfere with post-incident analysis and response."

